sentences.en: Objective To discuss the clinical effects of multiple segmental domelike decompression of the lumbar vertebral canal.
sentences.cn: 目的探讨多节段穹顶形开窗减压治疗腰椎管狭窄症的疗效。

sentences.en: To describe the clinical application of domelike decompression of the lumbar vertebral canal and evaluate the outcomes.
sentences.cn: 介绍穹顶形开窗减压术治疗腰椎管狭窄症的临床应用，并进行临床疗效评估及生物力学研究。
